#string STR_TRLR_RATIO0_OVERRIDE_HELP           #language en-US "Performance-core Turbo Ratio Limit Ratio0 (TRLR) with range of Max Non-Turbo Ratio to 120.This Turbo Ratio Limit Ratio0 must be greater than or equal all other ratio values. If this value is invalid, then set all other active cores to minimum. Otherwise, align the Ratio Limit to 0.\n\nPlease check each active cores"
