#string STR_TRLR_RATIO2_OVERRIDE_HELP           #language en-US "Performance-core Turbo Ratio Limit Ratio2 (TRLR) with range of Max Non-Turbo Ratio to 120.This Turbo Ratio Limit Ratio2 must be <= to Turbo Ratio Limit Ratio1."
