//
#string STR_CPPC_PROMPT                         #language en-US "ACPI 5.0 CPPC Support"
#string STR_CPPC_PROMPT_HELP                    #language en-US "Enable ACPI 5.0 Collaborative Processor Performance Control (CPPC) support. When Enabled, Platform exposes CPPC interfaces to Operating System. When Disabled, Platform exposes legacy (non-CPPC) processor interfaces to Operating System."
#string STR_CPPC_PLATFORMSCI_PROMPT             #language en-US "  ACPI 5.0 CPPC Platform SCI"
#string STR_CPPC_PLATFORMSCI_PROMPT_HELP        #language en-US "Enable ACPI 5.0 platform generation of SCI on CPPC command completion. When Enabled, Platform generates GPE/SCI. When Disabled, Platform does not generate GPE/SCI and OS polls for command completion."

